article.description: — Paul Scruggs had 14 points and nine assists as Xavier routed Tennessee Tech 79-48 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Scruggs lifts Xavier past Tennessee Tech 79-48
article.linkText: Scruggs lifts Xavier past Tennessee Tech 79-48
article.story: CINCINNATI -- — Paul Scruggs had 14 points and nine assists as Xavier routed Tennessee Tech 79-48 on Wednesday night. Zach Freemantle had 14 points for Xavier (5-0), which earned its fifth straight win to start the season. KyKy Tandy added 10 points. Kenny White Jr. had 13 points for the Golden Eagles (0-3). Austin Harvell added nine rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
